Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:14.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És que ho sabia. Al final s'ha perdut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:16.96,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ja fa molta estona que sé que m'he perdut!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:20.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "No fa gaire li he dit que havia de girar a l'esquerra."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:21.92,White,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:27.44,White,,0,0,0,,Allà hi ha una casa!Ah, sí? Estem salvats!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Uns ulls plorosos arriben el cor."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:38.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Les llàgrimes indiquen l'inici d'una tragèdia."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:40.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Una reunió de fans fanàtics,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,el misteri d'una sala tancada i la desaparició d'un ídol."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:47.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:49.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ano toki mita sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:51.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,furasshu bakku shita futo shita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:55.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Futoshita shunkan anata wo kanjita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:59.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kokoro no shattaa orikaketa no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:03.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,yuuhi ni ukanda anata no kao.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:10.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why, wakatteru no ni ienakatta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:17.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, soba ni ite hoshii I want your love.
